    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it runs beautifully and is ready for many more adventures. If you\u2019re looking for something dependable that looks great and won't let you down, this is the one. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see how smoothly it drives!",
      "price": 32500.0,
