      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies consistent maintenance and dependable performance. This well-appointed model offers a sophisticated driving experience, balancing mechanical integrity with a refined aesthetic. It represents a premier acquisition for the discerning driver seeking a reliable, high-value addition to their garage.",
      "price": 36800.0,
