    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and I think you're going to love it! It\u2019s in really lovely shape and has been super reliable for me. It drives so smoothly and the interior is still looking great\u2014I've definitely made sure to keep it tidy. It\u2019s a fantastic, dependable ride that\u2019s ready for many more adventures. If you\u2019re looking for a solid car that won't let you down, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
