    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This Porsche 911 Carrera (996.1) features the 3.4L water-cooled flat-six engine, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, supported by a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts. Recent preventative maintenance includes a retrofitted IMS bearing and a fresh rear main seal, ensuring the integrity of the M96 powerplant. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, providing exceptional thermal management. This example exhibits the tactile steering feedback and rear-biased weight distribution characteristic of the platform, making it a mechanically sound choice for the discerning driver.",
